OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,FStructural issues at a block of flats
OL,7,Fin Plymouth, which had to be evacuated
OL,8,Fover safety fears, could have been
OL,9,Fcaused by "incorrect construction" or
OL,10,F"inadequate design," a report has
OL,11,Frevealed.
OL,13,FPeople living in Evolution Cove were
OL,14,Fordered to leave their homes on Friday
OL,15,F20 March, after surveyors warned the
OL,16,Fbuilding could be at risk of collapse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,FA report by specialist engineering
OL,7,Ffirm, Clancy Consulting - seen
OL,8,Fexclusively by ITV News - has revealed
OL,9,Fevidence of "widespread cracking to
OL,10,Fstructural beams" in the 64-unit
OL,11,Fapartment block.
OL,13,FThe report also identified "a series
OL,14,Fof vertical hairline cracks" and
OL,15,F"shear cracking to transfer beams,"
OL,16,Falong with evidence of water leaks,
OL,17,Fpowdery concrete and overloading.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,FThe report, commissioned by the
OL,7,Fbuilding's owner Grey GR, found the
OL,8,Fproblems "could be caused by a number
OL,9,Fof factors, including the condition of
OL,10,Fthe concrete, or incorrect
OL,11,Fconstruction or inadequate design."
OL,13,F'It seems crazy that they didn't know'
OL,15,FResidents are still waiting to hear
OL,16,Fwhen they'll be allowed to return to
OL,17,Ftheir homes, and have been warned not
OL,18,Fto return to the building until the
OL,19,Fstructural issues have been resolved.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,FTenant Jon Dingle, who is still in
OL,7,Ftemporary accommodation elsewhere in
OL,8,Fthe city, said: "I'm no expert, but it
OL,9,Fdoes seem baffling that these things
OL,10,Fweren't picked up on before.
OL,12,F"I understand that when these types of
OL,13,Fbuildings are built - and it wasn't
OL,14,Fbuilt too long ago - that things need
OL,15,Fto be signed off on and inspections
OL,16,Fare done, so how come so many of these
OL,17,Fissues have been missed and we've
OL,18,Fended up in this situation?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,F"It just seems crazy to me that they
OL,7,Fdidn't know more. So I think there are
OL,8,Fa lot of questions that need to be
OL,9,Fasked, and hopefully people will have
OL,10,Fto face the consequences of their
OL,11,Factions."
OL,13,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService has placed a prohibition
OL,15,Fnotice on the building, and has warned
OL,16,Fthat anyone entering could face
OL,17,Fcriminal prosecution.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,FGroup manager Martin Sleigh said:
OL,7,F"This action has been taken to protect
OL,8,Flife. Working with partners,
OL,9,Fconsidering reports and advice from
OL,10,Fstructural engineers, our assessment
OL,11,Fwas that due to the structural
OL,12,Finstability, it would not be possible
OL,13,Ffor responders to safely help people
OL,14,Fin the building in the event of a
OL,15,Ffire, placing them at risk.
OL,17,F"A fire incident may make the building
OL,18,Fmore likely to collapse, which may
OL,19,Fprevent people from escaping."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,FAnyone found guilty of breaching the
OL,7,Forder could face up to two years in
OL,8,Fjail.
OL,10,FThe owner of the building, Grey GR,
OL,11,Fsaid it is working to make the
OL,12,Fstructure safe as soon as possible and
OL,13,Fthat residents' safety and wellbeing
OL,14,Fare the top priority.
OL,16,F'We understand the concern'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,FA spokesman for Grey GR said: "We
OL,7,Funderstand that residents are
OL,8,Fconcerned about the coming weeks, and
OL,9,Fwe are still expecting that residents
OL,10,Fwill be able to return to Evolution
OL,11,FCove within the eight-week estimate
OL,12,Fgiven when residents were evacuated on
OL,13,FMarch 20.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,F"We are expecting to shortly receive a
OL,7,Fprogramme of works for the back
OL,8,Fpropping installation, and if the
OL,9,Fcompletion date changes, residents
OL,10,Fwill be contacted as quickly as
OL,11,Fpossible, and alternative
OL,12,Faccommodation will continue to be
OL,13,Fprovided.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,F"Once back propping works have been
OL,7,Fcompleted, our structural engineers
OL,8,Fwill be able to carry out further
OL,9,Finvestigations and develop a
OL,10,Fremediation approach to reinforce the
OL,11,Fstructural integrity of the building.
OL,12,FOur focus is on ensuring this is
OL,13,Fcarried out as safely and
OL,14,Fcomprehensively as possible.
OL,16,F"We became aware of issues at the end
OL,17,Fof 2025, but at the time, structural
OL,18,Fengineers deemed the building safe for
OL,19,Fresidents to live in.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777551071
OL,3,C'Severe cracking' found in unstable
OL,4,Cflats as tenants warned to stay away
OL,6,F"When engineers revisited the building
OL,7,Fin March, they advised that immediate
OL,8,Fback propping was required. Due to the
OL,9,Fcomplexities of the works, this could
OL,10,Fnot be done straight away and
OL,11,Ftherefore advised an immediate
OL,12,Fevacuation.
OL,14,F"We understand the concern this
OL,15,Fcaused, but residents' safety and
OL,16,Fwellbeing are our top priority."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
